      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           subtract  1                    from v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lto                  .
           add       04                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      58                   to   v-pto                  .
