           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-dcf                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  all "."        to   rf-dcf-rag-soc
                     move  all "."        to   rf-dcf-via-dcf
                     move  all "."        to   rf-dcf-loc-dcf         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
